casebody.data:
Wednesday, September 29, 1999

MERIT DOCKET

99-1384. State ex rel. Vinci v. Mengel.

In Mandamus. On answer of respondent and on motion for judgment on pleadings. Answer treated as *1404motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnicic, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur. F.E. Sweeney, J., dissents and would grant the writ.
